profile: For all of your finishing, refinishing and furniture repair, we are the ones.  On top of our FREE estimates, pick up and delivery, we give each job our all!  Furniture is stripped, sanded, stained, sealed and lacquered all by hand; finished as if it were our own furniture.  Kitchens, dining rooms, bedrooms, antiques, you name it we do it.
